<main>
    <section class="page-hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Lab Coating Gauge</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container spec-sheet-container">
            <div class="breadcrumb">
                <a asp-page="/Products">‹ Back to Products</a>
            </div>

            <div class="spec-sheet-main">
                <div class="spec-sheet-content">
                    <h2>GaugeMaster for Lab Analysis</h2>
                    <p>As a final quality control checkpoint, our custom-built lab coating gauge provides precise offline analysis of coating weights. This bench-top instrument is used to verify coating weights on random samples from a finished coil, generating critical statistical data for quality assurance. Its simple, foot-pedal-operated interface allows for easy and reliable measurement by any user, ensuring consistent results without requiring specialized technical skill.</p>

                    <h3>Key Features</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Custom Built:</strong> Engineered specifically for offline sample analysis as a final QC step.</li>
                        <li><strong>User-Friendly Interface:</strong> Simple foot-pedal operation for quick and easy measurements.</li>
                        <li><strong>Versatile Measurement:</strong> Capable of analyzing Zinc, Galvanneal, Al-Zn (ZAM®), and Aluminum Types 1 & 2.</li>
                        <li><strong>Wide Substrate Range:</strong> Handles substrate thicknesses from 0.35 to 3.5 millimeters.</li>
                        <li><strong>Reliable & Robust:</strong> Built with the same high-quality components as our online systems for long-term accuracy.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="spec-sheet-image">
                    <figure>
                        <div class="spec-image-container aspect-ratio-lab">
                            <picture>
                                <source srcset="~/images/shared/rsi-benchtop-coating-gauge-500.webp" type="image/webp">
                                <img src="~/images/shared/rsi-benchtop-coating-gauge-500.jpg" alt="RSI Lab Coating Gauge for offline sampling">
                            </picture>
                        </div>
                        <figcaption>RSI's custom-built GaugeMaster Lab Coating Gauge.</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-sheet-gallery">
                <h3>Additional Images</h3>
                <div class="gallery-grid">
                    <figure>
                        <img src="~/images/products/rsi-main-electronics-cabinet-technician-terminal.jpg" alt="RSI Main Electronics Cabinet">
